menuconfig GZRL
	bool "GZRL robot library"
	help
	  Enable the GMaster Zephyr Robot Library integration layer.

	  The initial module provides project scaffolding and a smoke sample only.
	  Future GZRL subsystems select their own configuration symbols beneath this
	  top-level option.
